summary: Educated in South Africa (grades 1 to 12) and achieved my National Senior Certificate in 2018. Then went to Croatia to obtain certification for instruction of PADI Courses and gain experience in the water with students and certified divers alike in 2019. Returned to South Africa to complete STCW and Compressor Operator Courses. Followed STCW course with RYA Powerboat Level 2 course, after which I returned to Croatia to work as a SCUBA Instructor and Dive Boat Operator (2020). Started studying Civil Engineering at HZ University of Applied Sciences in 2021.
